Pomeroy, Robert D. - The Wall Street Transcript











































 





































Robert D. Pomeroy
Robert D. Pomeroy Jr. is CEO and Chairman of the board of Horizon Technology Finance Corporation, a public, externally managed business development company. His background includes positions as President of GATX Ventures, Inc., and Co-Founder and Executive Vice President of Transamerica Business Credit’s technology finance division. Earlier, he served as Senior Vice President with Financing for Science International, Inc. Mr. Pomeroy has over 35 years of diversified lending and leasing experience. He earned both an MBA and B.S. from the University of California, Berkeley.
